node.text:
How lucky am I to have a mom who makes the best biryani around? This prawn biryani for lunch was so satisfying that I think I'll just be eating salad for dinner. 😀 Oh, and there is leftover for tomorrow too, though sorry, no visiting to steal some. 😜 #circuitbreakersg #stayathome
